### takeRight

Use `Array.slice()` to create a slice of the array with `n` elements taken from the end.

```js
const takeRight = (arr, n = 1) => arr.slice(arr.length - n, arr.length);
// takeRight([1, 2, 3], 2) -> [ 2, 3 ]
// takeRight([1, 2, 3]) -> [3]
// takeRight([1, 2, 3], 0) -> []
```
